R and Shiny are NOT distributed
================================================================================
R and any R packages (including Shiny) are NOT distributed with shinylaunchR.
They are downloaded and installed on the user's machine from CRAN at runtime,
under their own licenses (R: GPL-2/GPL-3; Shiny: GPL-3). shinylaunchR launches
R as a separate process and does not embed, link, or redistribute R or its
packages. For transparency, R's license and sources are at
https://www.r-project.org/Licenses/ and https://cran.r-project.org/.

